column1: gtfo_on_desc;The Release Vassal decisions allow you to release vassals
column2: and are otherwise kept hidden from view to avoid having them clutter up your decision list.;;;;;;;;;;;;x

column1: gtfo_off_desc;Your decision list will now be uncluttered!;;;;;;;;;;;;x
gtfo_disabled_desc;The 'Release Vassal' decisions will disappear from this game session and won't reappear again. You won't be able to use these decisions again for this game.;;;;;;;;;;;;x
